select_plug.title: Please take a look
select_plug.description: This charging station allows you to charge with DC and AC plug types. Select the plug you will like to use.

support.title: Have questions?
support.description: To contact our support team, please select one of the options below.

terms_and_conditions.title: Terms of use
terms_and_conditions.description: To use the application, it is mandatory to accept the service terms and conditions and privacy policy

descriptions.tc: I hereby confirm that I have read and accept the Enel X <0>Terms and Conditions.</0>
descriptions.privacy_policy: I hereby confirm that I have read the Enel X <0>Privacy policy.</0>

authorization_fail.title: Authorization fail
authorization_fail.description: We were unable to pre-authorize your payment method. Make sure the entered information is correct and try again.

invoice_information.title: Invoice Information
invoice_information.description: An invoice can be issued in your name for tax purposes. Add your personal information to have it included with the invoice. You may not add it after the transaction is complete.

idle_fee.title: Idle fee
idle_fee.description: Idle fees up to {{value}}/min may apply if you don't unplug and move your car at the end of charging.

mail.title: Provide your email
mail.description: Please provide your email address to continue.

connection_status.title: Plug in your car
connection_status.description: To start charing, please plug in your car within {{value}} seconds.

connection_to_station.title: Connection to station
connection_to_station.description: We had trouble connecting to this station to start your charging session. Your credit card was not charged. Please try again to start the session or find another available station.

session_timeout.title: Session time out
session_timeout.description: You failed to plug the cable to the charging station on time. You will be redirected back to the map, from where you can try again.

connected.advice: Do not close this browser window! Please keep this browser window open in order to see the status of charge, to stop charging or get an invoice.
connected.warning: Please unplug and move your car!

session_completed.title: Session completed
session_completed.description: Your session is completed. Please check your invoice by accessing the link we sent to your email.
